END GOAL

The final system should be capable of generating high-quality EDM and hip-hop songs, predicting listener engagement, continuously improving based on listener data, and producing professional-quality tracks at scale.

The result is a self-improving AI music engine capable of generating viral music and tracks optimized for both streaming platforms and live DJ performances.